      <title>英国经济学家称市场对降息的押注错误</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/uk-economists-say-markets-betting-wrong-on-interest-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英格兰银行发现自己陷入了大西洋两岸关于谁将首先降息的分歧，这对指望选举年缓解高借贷成本的英国国债交易商和英国政治领导人造成了高昂的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/uk-economists-say-markets-betting-wrong-on-interest-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
