      <title>罢工后中东紧张局势缓和，金价回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/gold-backtracks-as-middle-east-tensions-ease-following-strikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着中东地缘政治紧张局势缓和、避险需求减少，以及交易员期待美国数据将揭示货币政策前景，金价回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/gold-backtracks-as-middle-east-tensions-ease-following-strikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 02:03:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于交易员关注中东风险，油价在每周下跌后下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-22</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在今年首次连续一周下跌后下跌，因交易商在中东紧张局势不断升温的情况下权衡伊朗和以色列可能采取的下一步行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-22</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 23:30:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
